{"tid":2366322,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家齊齊比d創意參加[香港島婦女聯會 撐警活動]","createTime":"2021-01-14T11:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T13:00:41.000Z","uid":6489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13b505cd45026f14a0c457bc7125fb8cfabce70d","tid":2366322,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"大家一齊參加下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家一定有好多靚相同片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿Sir與我的故事----感恩警察活動<br />\n<br />\n過去一年香港社會動蕩逐漸平息，社會秩序恢復穩定，離不開香港警察的奮勇捍衛和默默的堅守。時值新春佳節之際，本會舉辦 &quot;阿Sir謝謝你&quot;活動，誠邀大家將香港警員的感謝以各種形式表達出來。届時本會將大家的祝福集合成視頻於2月初送給警署。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n主題：阿Sir與我的故事----感恩警察活動<br />\n内容：給街頭工作的警察點贊，拍照留影，將自己對香港警察的感謝與祝福表達出來。<br />\n參與形式：以視頻，照片，文字的形式將&quot;阿Sir與我的故事&quot;發至hkiwassoc@yahoo.com或Whatsapp至94332232 （作品注明姓名）<br />\n截至日期：2021年1月31日<br />\n獎品: 評選出「最暖心畫面與瞬間」一、二、三名 ，贏取豐富的新春抗疫禮包福袋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaUT4Se.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaUT4Se.png&h=34e7a3d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9168f6367102e4fe24fe8cc8261481b241b322eb","tid":2366322,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db22eae2593ddf7790a19d35e68baf5904bf0ec5","tid":2366322,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"仆街廢老聯會"},{"pid":"51211316f7e2d3016c4dd15a79a669b2fc7d3d53","tid":2366322,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-